            with a freelancer. Highly recommend Mikael!
          </p>
        </Testimonial>
        <Testimonial
          author={{
            name: "Spencer Smith",
            title: "Principal Data Scientist, Zillow Group, Founder, BenAi",
            avatar: "testimonials/spencer-smith.jpg",
            url: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/spencergsmith6/",
          }}
