          </p>
        </Testimonial>
        <Testimonial
          author={{
            name: "Victor Meyer",
            title: "Co-Founder and Creative Web Developer, Pixby Media",
            avatar: "testimonials/victor-meyer.jpg",
            url: "https://www.linkedin.com/in/victor-meyer-9784702b/",
          }}
        >
          <p>
            It's been a privilege to work alongside Mikael for the past 15
            years. He's not only an exceptional developer and mentor but also
